From 3a6078aae2793775bd0b8b624c3221fe78fc1b5b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: liuyuyan6100 <liuyuyan6100@163.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 08:39:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] feat: auto JWT login for Sub2API admin endpoints

Sub2API v0.1.114+ switched admin auth from x-api-key to Bearer JWT.
This patch adds automatic admin login when SUB2API_ADMIN_EMAIL and
SUB2API_ADMIN_PASSWORD are configured, and transparently retries
401 requests with a fresh Bearer token.
---
 utils/integrations/sub2api_client.py | 149 +++++++++++++++++----------
 1 file changed, 97 insertions(+), 52 deletions(-)

